Package com.intellij.xdebugger.breakpoints

Interface XBreakpoint<P extends XBreakpointProperties>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    UserDataHolder
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    XLineBreakpoint<P>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    XBreakpointBase, XLineBreakpointImpl

    public interface XBreakpoint<P extends XBreakpointProperties>
extends UserDataHolder
    Represents a breakpoint. This interface isn't supposed to be implemented by a plugin. In order to support breakpoint provide XBreakpointType or XLineBreakpointType implementation
    See Also:
    XLineBreakpoint, XBreakpointManager
